[30;1m138 | [0m[35m## Everything is a Mutable Mapping[0m
[30;1m139 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m140 | [0m[35m... or at least everything that can be imported/exported from/to a json blob[0m
[30;1m141 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m142 | [0m[35m`AbstractMISP` is the master class, and inherits from `collections.MutableMapping` which means[0m
[30;1m143 | [0m[35mthe class can be represented as a python dictionary.[0m
